Something terrible
has to happen.

5
00:00:07,379 --> 00:00:09,783
I'm sorry my accomplishments
happen in broad daylight

6
00:00:09,877 --> 00:00:11,930
and I can't be given
the same rewards.

7
00:00:12,654 --> 00:00:14,054
I'm sorry, but your
name escapes me.

